# ChirpNet

ChirpNet is a small Twitter-like social network built as a final ASP.NET Core MVC project.

The application allows users to create short posts, view a public feed, comment on posts, like/unlike posts through AJAX, follow/unfollow other users, manage their own posts, search users and posts, and access admin-only functionality.

## Technologies Used

- ASP.NET Core MVC
- ASP.NET Core Identity
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server
- Docker SQL Server container
- Razor Views
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript Fetch API / AJAX
- NUnit
- EF Core InMemory provider for tests

## Main Features

### Public Features

- Home page
- Public feed
- Post details page
- Search users and posts
- User profile pages

### Authenticated User Features

- Register and login
- Create posts
- Edit own posts
- Delete own posts
- Comment on posts
- Like and unlike posts with AJAX
- Follow and unfollow users
- View My Posts page

### Admin Features

- Seeded Administrator role
- Seeded admin account
- Protected admin dashboard
- Admin post management
- Soft delete and restore posts

