Project Architecture

The solution is separated into multiple projects:

ChirpNet.Web

Contains the ASP.NET Core MVC application, controllers, views, static files, Identity pages, and application startup configuration.

ChirpNet.Data

Contains the Entity Framework Core DbContext, entity models, EF Core configurations, migrations, and database seeding logic.

ChirpNet.Services

Contains service interfaces, service implementations, and service models. Business logic is placed here instead of inside controllers.

ChirpNet.Tests

Contains NUnit tests for the service layer.

